    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "[Clause 5c](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/apps/hh694058.aspx) of the Windows App Developer Agreement bans OpenRA from the Windows app store because we have not explicitly licenced the C&C intellectual property from EA.  I imagine that most other open source engine recreations for proprietary games (OpenTTD, OpenRCT2, etc) will be in a similar situation.\r\n\r\nSo sorry, this simply isn't possible."
